-04_at_9.59.00_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1743818354/Screenshot_2025-04-04_at_9.59.00_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Coach Artie interface\" width=\"3358\" height=\"1884\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.76deg;\" data-dimensions=\"3358×1884\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-video w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Coach Artie interface</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Coach Artie in conversation\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1757894550/screenshot_2025-09-14_at_8.02.18_PM.png\" alt=\"Coach Artie in conversation\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1757894550/screenshot_2025-09-14_at_8.02.18_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1757894550/screenshot_2025-09-14_at_8.02.18_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1757894550/screenshot_2025-09-14_at_8.02.18_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1757894550/screenshot_2025-09-14_at_8.02.18_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Coach Artie in conversation\" width=\"1774\" height=\"810\" style=\"--splay-rot:2.45deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1774×810\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Coach Artie in conversation</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Coach Artie ecosystem view\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1740247476/Screenshot_2025-02-22_at_1.04.24_PM.png\" alt=\"Coach Artie ecosystem view\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1740247476/Screenshot_2025-02-22_at_1.04.24_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1740247476/Screenshot_2025-02-22_at_1.04.24_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1740247476/Screenshot_2025-02-22_at_1.04.24_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1740247476/Screenshot_2025-02-22_at_1.04.24_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Coach Artie ecosystem view\" width=\"3600\" height=\"2252\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.86deg;\" data-dimensions=\"3600×2252\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Coach Artie ecosystem view</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<h2 class=\"\" id=\"coach-artie-v1-discord-studio-assistant\">Coach Artie v1: Discord Studio Assistant</h2>\n<p class=\"\">I created <a href=\"https://coachartiebot.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\" data-preview-url=\"https://coachartiebot.com\">Coach Artie</a> to serve as our Discord studio assistant. He's evolved into a powerful AI tool with persistent memory and tool usage - helping our team coordinate and manage creative workflows.</p>\n<h2 class=\"\" id=\"coach-artie-v2-production-ai-with-mcp-tools\">Coach Artie v2: Production AI with MCP Tools</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Currently in development.</p>\n<h2 class=\"\" id=\"memory--consciousness-analysis\">Memory &#x26; Consciousness Analysis</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Explores AI consciousness emergence through memory patterns with scientific rigor applied to existential questions. This research component investigates how persistent memory systems in AI assistants might lead to emergent conscious-like behaviors.</p>\n<h3 class=\"\" id=\"related-content\">Related Content</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-disc\">\n<li class=\"\"><a href=\"https://youtube.com/@ejfox\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\" data-preview-url=\"https://youtube.com/@ejfox\">The AI-Human Creative Loop: My 2025 Working Process<svg class=\"inline-block w-4 h-4 ml-1 opacity-50 dark:opacity-75 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity align-text-bottom\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M23.498 6.186a3.02 3.02 0 0 0-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.02 3.02 0 0 0 .502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.02 3.02 0 0 0 2.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.02 3.02 0 0 0 2.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814M9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12z\" class=\"\"></path></svg></a> - How AI assistants integrate into continuous creative workflows</li>\n<li class=\"\"><a href=\"https://youtube.com/@ejfox\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\" data-preview-url=\"https://youtube.com/@ejfox\">AI Is Our Newest Drug<svg class=\"inline-block w-4 h-4 ml-1 opacity-50 dark:opacity-75 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity align-text-bottom\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M23.498 6.186a3.02 3.02 0 0 0-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.02 3.02 0 0 0 .502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.02 3.02 0 0 0 2.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.02 3.02 0 0 0 2.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814M9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12z\" class=\"\"></path></svg></a> - Philosophical exploration of AI as psychoactive technology</li>\n</ul>",
